description: Dashboard for results of load testing

targets.query: SELECT mean("planned_requests") FROM "${test_id}_overall_meta" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1s) fill(null)
SELECT mean("planned_requests") FROM "${test_id}_overall_meta" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1s) fill(null)
SELECT mean("RPS") FROM "${test_id}_overall_meta" WHERE ("label"::tag = '${endpoint}') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1s) fill(null)
SELECT sum(*) AS "HTTP" FROM "${test_id}_proto_codes" WHERE ("label"::tag = '${endpoint}') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT sum(*) as "CODE" FROM "${test_id}_net_codes" WHERE ("label"::tag = '${endpoint}') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT max("q${quantile}") AS "q${quantile}" FROM "autogen"."${test_id}_overall_quantiles" WHERE ("label" != '__OVERALL__') and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "label"::tag fill(null)
SELECT mean("RPS") AS "Responses per second" FROM "autogen"."${test_id}_overall_meta" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT mean("planned_requests") AS "Requests per second" FROM "autogen"."${test_id}_overall_meta" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean("200") AS "http_200", mean("500") AS "http_500", mean("429") AS "http_429" FROM "${test_id}_proto_codes" WHERE ("label"::tag = '${endpoint}') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT mean("RPS") FROM "${test_id}_overall_meta" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT mean("planned_requests") AS "Requests per second" FROM "autogen"."${test_id}_overall_meta" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT (sum("500") / (sum("500") + sum("200")) * 100) AS "HTTP" FROM "${test_id}_proto_codes" WHERE ("label"::tag = '${endpoint}') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(20s) fill(null)
SELECT mean("RPS") FROM "${test_id}_overall_meta" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT mean("planned_requests") AS "Requests per second" FROM "autogen"."${test_id}_overall_meta" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT (sum("429") / (sum("429") + sum("200")) * 100) AS "HTTP" FROM "${test_id}_proto_codes" WHERE ("label"::tag = '${endpoint}') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(20s) fill(null)
SELECT mean("active_threads") FROM "${test_id}_overall_meta" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean("planned_requests") AS "Requests per second" FROM "${test_id}_overall_meta" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean("planned_requests") AS "Requests per second" FROM "${test_id}_overall_meta" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
